<p>I'll be walking in the Heart Walk this year, and I'm pulling together donations. Please consider donating for this wonderful cause.</p>
<img src="http://www.faia.com/core/contentmanager/uploads/About%20FAIA/Images/Staff/Steve-Hirstcolor.gif" style="padding: 3px; float: left;" />
<p>We recently lost a co-worker, <a href="http://www.faia.com/web/2007/11/stephen_r_hirst.aspx" target="_blank">Steve Hirst</a>, to a heart attack this year. He passed away shortly after snorkeling in Key West. I'm sure many others have similar stories about a friend or family member lost to some sort of heart disease.</p>
<p>While raising the most money is usually awarded with prizes, I have opted out of all prizes to enable as much as the donations as possible to go to the Heart Association's work.</p>
